DeAnna Robbins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DeAnna_Robbins 0 DeAnna Robbins (born June 7, 1959) is an American actress best known for her role as Lisa in the 1981 slasher film Final Exam, and for her role as Kathleen McDougall on the soap opera Santa Barbara, for which she appeared in 17 episodes.
